ss="size-full wp-image-3472761" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270.jpg" alt="艾德·希兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ed-sheeran@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3472761" class="wp-caption-text">艾德·希兰。图片来源：Theo Wargo/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>随后两人表演了阿姆 2000 年的歌曲《Stan》，希兰填补了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dido">迪多</a>的部分。</p><p>希兰<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-says-listening-to-eminem-helped-cure-his-stutter-3442849">此前曾称赞阿姆帮助他“治愈”了童年的口吃</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-expresses-his-fears-over-weird-ai-technology-3479746">希兰最近公开了他对在音乐中使用人工智能的想法</a>，称这项技术“很奇怪”。</p><p> “我对人工智能的不理解之处在于，过去 60 年来，好莱坞电影一直在告诉你，‘不要这样做’。现在每个人都在这样做，”这位音乐家在纽约硬石酒店接受<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5IFUXNfqqcY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Audacy</a>采访时说道。 “我就想，‘你没看过他们杀死我们所有人的电影吗？’”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ed-sheeran-sing-lego-house-outside-a-lego-shop-in-minnesota-3482096">观看艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 在明尼苏达州乐高商店外演唱《乐高屋》(Lego House) 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
