新弗雷迪·墨丘利 (Freddie Mercury) 展览在伦敦苏富比拍卖行开幕https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-freddie-mercury-exhibition-launched-at-sothebys-london-3482070?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=new-freddie-mercury-exhibition-launched-at-伦敦苏富比Hollie GeraghtySun, 13 Aug 2023 15:57:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3482070 <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗雷迪·摩克瑞" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>亮点包括女王主唱的标志性皇冠和斗篷合奏以及他的雅马哈三角钢琴</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-freddie-mercury-exhibition-launched-at-sothebys-london-3482070">在伦敦苏富比拍卖行举办的新弗雷迪·墨丘利 (New Freddie Mercury) 展览</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗雷迪·摩克瑞" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Freddie-Mercury-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/freddie-mercury">弗雷迪·墨丘利 (Freddie Mercury)</a>的新展览在伦敦举办，展出已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>乐队主唱的个人物品。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/queens-freddie-mercury-the-maddest-stories-about-rocks-best-loved-hellraiser-769352">皇后乐队的 Freddie Mercury：有关摇滚乐最受欢迎的地狱崛起的最疯狂的故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 4 月份，就有消息称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/freddie-mercury-personal-belongings-auction-3436247">苏富比将于今年 9 月将 Mercury 位于伦敦的家中的 1,400 件物品（该家已经 30 年未曾动过）进行拍卖</a>。</p><p>包括手写歌词、个人宝丽莱照片和服装在内的大量藏品现已在伦敦展出。</p><p> “今年夏天，我们邀请您在伦敦苏富比拍卖行的长期收购中走进弗雷迪·墨丘利的个人世界，”网站上写道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3436250" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3436250" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3436250" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270.jpg" alt="弗雷迪·摩克瑞" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/freddie-mercury-crown@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3436250" class="wp-caption-text"> 1986 年，弗雷迪·墨丘利 (Freddie Mercury) 与皇后乐队在伦敦温布利体育场演出。图片来源：Denis O&#39;Regan/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位女王乐队主唱于 1991 年 11 月 24 日在伦敦去世，他将自己位于肯辛顿的花园别墅 (Garden Lodge) 的家和财产留给了密友玛丽·奥斯汀 (Mary Austin)，目前玛丽·奥斯汀正在与公众分享这些物品。</p><p> “Freddie Mercury：他自己的世界”展览的亮点包括 Mercury 在 1986 年“魔法之旅”中所佩戴的<a href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/buy/auction/2023/freddie-mercury-a-world-of-his-own-the-evening-sale/freddie-mercurys-signature-crown-and-cloak-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">王冠和斗篷</a>套装、他的<a href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/buy/auction/2023/freddie-mercury-a-world-of-his-own-the-evening-sale/freddie-mercurys-stage-worn-kimono-1976" target="_blank" rel="noopener">红色和服</a>，上面布满了扇子，以及他创作了“We Are The” <a href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/buy/auction/2023/freddie-mercury-a-world-of-his-own-the-evening-sale/the-instrument-used-to-compose-some-of-the" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的雅马哈三角钢琴</a>冠军。后者预计价值 200 万至 300 万英镑（来自<em><a href="https://news.sky.com/story/freddie-mercury-fans-crying-and-fainting-as-1-400-of-his-possessions-go-on-show-12939059" target="_blank" rel="noopener">天空新闻</a></em>）。</p><p>藏品中的其他物品包括皇后乐队 1975 年热门歌曲《波西米亚狂想曲》的手写草稿、日本花瓶、萨尔瓦多·达利的艺术品、记录宾客名单和晚宴计划的笔记本、阿迪达斯高帮运动鞋以及他整个舞台生涯的服装。</p><p>苏富比的 15 个画廊中的每一个都将致力于墨丘利生活的不同方面，游客可以在他的卧室、酒吧和餐厅的娱乐场所中漫步。</p><p>苏富比欧洲主席奥利弗·巴克 (Oliver Barker) 告诉<em>天空新闻</em>，粉丝们因展览而哭泣和晕倒。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/Sothebys?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Sothebys</a>的弗雷迪·墨丘利 (Freddie Mercury) 展览非常出色，并且完全免费参观 - 每天开放直至 9 月 5 日。 <a href="https://t.co/DvehA3ihAr">https://t.co/DvehA3ihAr</a> <a href="https://t.co/4kF8t1h8J3">pic.twitter.com/4kF8t1h8J3</a></p><p> — ianVisits (@ianvisits) <a href="https://twitter.com/ianvisits/status/1687453187895169024?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 4 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “我认为这有点不同，”他说。</p><p> “我认为这是因为弗雷迪是如此受人尊敬，而且我认为我们正在展示他生活的私人生活，与公共生活相反，这是以前从未探索过的。</p><p> “所以我真诚地认为这是考古学历史的一部分，正在发生。”</p><p>展览时间为8月4日至9月5日， <a href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/series/freddie-mercury-a-world-of-his-own-exhibition-plan-your-visit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费向公众开放，无需预约</a>。</p><p>这些物品将从 9 月 6 日起在六场拍卖会上出售。您可以<a href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/auction-catalogue/2023/freddie-mercury-a-world-of-his-own-the-evening-sale?s=intro" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到更多详细信息</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-freddie-mercury-exhibition-launched-at-sothebys-london-3482070">在伦敦苏富比拍卖行举办的新弗雷迪·墨丘利 (New Freddie Mercury) 展览</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《速度与激情》主演泰瑞斯·吉布森因涉嫌种族歧视起诉家得宝，索赔 100 万美元https://www.nme.com/news/film/fast-and-furious-star-tyrese-gibson-sues-home-depot-for-1m-over-alleged-racial-profiling-3482033?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=速度与激情明星泰瑞斯·吉布森起诉家得宝 100 多万人涉嫌种族剖析Damian JonesSun, 13 Aug 2023 15:05:29 +0000 Film NewsNewsfast and furious https://www.nme.com/?p=3482033 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国演员泰瑞斯·吉布森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周早些时候在洛杉矶提起诉讼</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fast-and-furious-star-tyrese-gibson-sues-home-depot-for-1m-over-alleged-racial-profiling-3482033">《速度与激情》主演泰瑞斯·吉布森因涉嫌种族歧视而起诉家得宝 100 万美元</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国演员泰瑞斯·吉布森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/fast-and-furious"><em>《速度与激情》</em></a>明星泰瑞斯·吉布森因涉嫌种族歧视而起诉美国五金店家得宝 (The Home Depot)，索赔超过 100 万美元（合 79 万英镑）。</p><p>这位曾出演过七部大片的演员声称，他和两名同事在二月份的一次事件中遭受了“令人发指的歧视性虐待”。</p><p>本周早些时候在洛杉矶提起的一项诉讼详细说明了据称发生在洛杉矶县西山家得宝商店的事件。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/tyrese-gibson-sues-home-depot-racial-profiling-1235694090/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，这起事件涉及吉布森、埃里克·莫拉和曼努埃尔·埃尔南德斯，他们因“据称的系统故障”而被拘留。</p><p>三人投诉称，这导致他们在大约 20 分钟内无法结帐，然后结账台周围开始出现人群。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cvzj1j4ASCx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns=